{"tid":2148753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸首款千元 5G 手機   將採用國產虎賁處理器","createTime":"2020-08-10T05:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T02:09:50.000Z","uid":225931,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2126aa83125d222d65abf04abdc6435be1d9fc37","tid":2148753,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"中國大陸的 5G 服務雖然在去年年底才正式推出，但至今已經有不少 5G 手機在市場銷售，雖然大部份 5G 手機都屬於旗艦級或中階手機，但首款千元 5G 手機據說會在本週三（8 月 12 日）發表，而售價低於現今市場水平的原因，相信與使用的處理器有關。<br />\n<br />\n大陸手機品牌酷派（Coolpad）日前宣佈，將會在週三舉行發佈會，正式公佈千元 5G 手機 Coolpad X10。這是酷派與中國電信合作的手機，採用的是紫光展銳（Unisoc）的國產 5G 處理器「虎賁 T7510」。該處理器使用 12nm 工藝製程，由 Cortex A75 四核和 Cortex A55 四核組成，搭配 PowerVR GM9446 圖像處理器，在 5G 模式下最高上下載速率為 1Gbps 和 2Gbps。<br />\n<br />\nCoolpad X10 手機的詳情要到 8 月 12 日發佈會才公開，但 Unisoc 的新一代「虎賁 T7520」5G 處理器則早前已經發表，不但採用 6nm 製程，由 A76 四核和 A55 四核組成，就連上下載速度亦達到 1.25Gbps 和 3.25Gbps，不過至今尚未開始量產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ek21.com/news/tech/209637/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fek21.com%2Fnews%2Ftech%2F209637%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=1a83d1d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ek21.com/news/tech/209637/</a>"},{"pid":"11ef97122f724da7a17fbe6946a9fca90905e652","tid":2148753,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"苦噴？"},{"pid":"aada141ce980a2f04fecf968ab8123e272ef1e83","tid":2148753,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11ef97122f724da7a17fbe6946a9fca90905e652","tid":2148753,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"苦噴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"苦墳"},{"pid":"d0a727eeeb3ba4d5927516889385343c3ac289fc","tid":2148753,"uid":293472,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">不過至今尚未開始量產</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wo